{"tid":929540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網友在DIA豫彬貼文留下惡評：「只有有人氣的才受到IU喜愛」而IU也親自來回覆，直接打臉惡評啦！","createTime":"2018-12-05T16:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T07:11:30.000Z","uid":34643,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"771f7a527abae42ce60c071630636bc8016d3a26","tid":929540,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_814b430d864b1a0bb3964e8a00964aea/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-12-05/111862-683426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_814b430d864b1a0bb3964e8a00964aea%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-12-05%2F111862-683426.jpg&h=669fa704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這真的讓留下惡評的人無話可說了，帥氣又善良的IU啊！<br />\n<br />\nDIA成員豫彬翻唱了IU的《雙唇之間》並把影片上傳到IG：「今天的推薦曲雖然還有很多的不足，終於試著唱了IU前輩的《雙唇之間》。」豫彬從以前就很喜歡和尊敬IU，日前IU10週年演唱會豫彬也有到場，還送了花給IU，兩人還在後台一起合照了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_585d6086d5a3862649af730853807a34/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-12-05/111862-683424.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_585d6086d5a3862649af730853807a34%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-12-05%2F111862-683424.png&h=90821c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_32f7603aef39fcfbbe386b571a131a04/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-12-05/111862-683425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_32f7603aef39fcfbbe386b571a131a04%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-12-05%2F111862-683425.jpg&h=854c0d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這則貼文引來酸民留言：「你知道IU給TWICE的娜璉送了禮物嗎？只有有人氣的才受到IU喜愛，但豫彬不是，打起精神吧！看起來很可憐。」豫彬回覆他：「是我喜歡才這麼做的，沒有關係。」結果IU親自來回覆：「讚和愛心（表情符號）。」豫彬也開心地回覆IU：「天啊....前輩Nim。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_745f92e9d5b6335fea0b3c9e8bca642b/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-12-05/111862-683422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_745f92e9d5b6335fea0b3c9e8bca642b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-12-05%2F111862-683422.jpg&h=90cb00ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU的回覆也在網路上引發熱議，網友們都表示：「知恩啊！真的太帥了」、「寫惡評給別人留下傷害的人，他的人生才可憐」、「IU好棒」、「直接打臉惡評了呢」等等，只能說寫惡評的人真的太無聊了。另外，也有網友提到：「TWICE會收到禮物，是因為當了IU演唱會嘉賓，IU作為感謝才送的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5523fddbe03449beabec8039da667a18/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-12-05/111862-683427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5523fddbe03449beabec8039da667a18%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-12-05%2F111862-683427.png&h=00dee30a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b07c569da10aa39cfb1ee1c2492636e1066a1de7","tid":929540,"uid":74065,"like":53,"dislike":5,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"D娜璉粉真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3ef23fd6cc3a473e85de36312290d16753d840","tid":929540,"uid":89660,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"b07c569da10aa39cfb1ee1c2492636e1066a1de7","tid":929540,"uid":74065,"like":53,"dislike":5,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"D娜璉粉真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"條友擺明你啲frd黎啦死黑粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d503e759dbf38594433b3249c908dfe5f8838f1b","tid":929540,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc3ef23fd6cc3a473e85de36312290d16753d840","tid":929540,"uid":89660,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"b07c569da10aa39cfb1ee1c2492636e1066a1de7","tid":929540,"uid":74065,"like":53,"dislike":5,"score":48,